name: Renewed PT today (J)
query:
SELECT old_pawn_ticket as "Old pawn ticket", workflow_state as "Status", pawn_ticket as "New pawn ticket", date_loan_granted as "Date loan granted", desired_principal as " New PT Principal"
FROM `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`
WHERE `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.docstatus=1
AND `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.old_pawn_ticket IS NOT NULL
AND `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.date_loan_granted = CURDATE()
AND `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.branch = 'Garcia\'s Pawnshop - MOL'
